        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Yuan Yue Yue agrees to marry wealthy heir Wen Jin Chen to cover for her sister’s past mistake. On the wedding day, she’s shocked to find photos of herself displayed at the venue and discovers that Wen Jin Chen is delayed. In a panic, she decides to flee, hijacking a car without realizing Wen Jin Chen is inside. Once she discovers the truth, they have a confrontation, but when a car thief\n\nsteals their vehicle, Yuan Yue Yue chases him down, impressing Wen Jin Chen. As pressure to marry intensifies, can these rocky beginnings spark a genuine romance?",
